{"type":"message","id":"7f12f155","parentId":"14f27568","timestamp":"2026-03-22T07:58:24.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user files are mostly empty - USER.md has no info filled in, and MEMORY.md and memory files don't exist yet. But there's a BOOTSTRAP.md file that exists - this means I'm in a fresh workspace and should follow the bootstrap process.\n\nLet me read the BOOTSTRAP.md file to see what I should do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0c5655cda2044c8a8aa23089","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/userli/.openclaw/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7702,"output":162,"cacheRead":5504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774166300273}}
{"type":"message","id":"fecc44a7","parentId":"7f12f155","timestamp":"2026-03-22T07:58:24.651Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0c5655cda2044c8a8aa23089","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774166304650}}
{"type":"message","id":"33239bbe","parentId":"fecc44a7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T07:58:34.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a fresh workspace - BOOTSTRAP.md exists and the user hasn't filled in their details yet. According to the bootstrap instructions, I should have a conversation to figure out who I am and who they are.\n\nThe user said \"你好\" (hello in Chinese), so they're speaking Chinese. I should respond in Chinese and start the bootstrap conversation naturally.\n\nLet me greet them and start figuring out who we are together.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我刚醒来。我是谁？你是谁？\n\n来聊聊吧 —— 你想让我叫什么名字？我是个什么样的存在？(AI 助手也行，但也许可以更有趣一点) 🤔"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":486,"output":219,"cacheRead":13184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13889,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774166304652}}
